nodes.text: Nathan Blyskipper was a Human male who worked as a junk dealer in Mos Taike on Tatooine during the Galactic Civil War

Nathan Blyskipper was a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
